Turkey.title: Harmonized Index of Consumer Prices: Passenger Transport by Railway for Turkey
Turkey.notes:
The Harmonized Index of Consumer Prices category "Passenger Transport by Railway (07.3.1)" is a classification of services that includes transport of individuals and groups of persons and luggage by train, tram, and underground; and transport of private vehicles.

Passenger Transport by Railway (07.3.1) excludes funicular transport (07.3.6).

This category is a subcategory of the Transport (07) and of Transport Services (07.3) categories.

Information provided in the notes pertaining to HICP classifications can be found from the source at: http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/cache/metadata/en/prc_hicp_esms.htm.
